data.description: This beautiful single-family home has so much to offer! You are welcomed by a covered front porch overlooking the yard! Walk into the living room featuring gorgeous hardwood floors that continue throughout the home, and a fireplace! Off of the living room is the formal dining room with lovely built-in shelving with glass cabinets perfect for displaying and extra storage! The large picture windows in the dining room allow for natural light! Continue through to the kitchen that offers plenty of counterspace and lovely tiled backsplash! Off of the living room there is an additional room that is perfect for an office or additional living space! 2 of the bedrooms are downstairs along with the full bathroom! Upstairs you will find 2 incredibly spacious bedrooms featuring large windows allowing for tons of natural light! The basement offers tons of space for storage, a laundry area and a convenient full bathroom! Outside there is a gorgeous deck that is perfect for entertaining and a 2-car garage! With easy highways access this is close to Downtown Cleveland and near food, shopping and public transit! This won't last long! Schedule a showing to see it for yourself!
